# Power BI Projects Portfolio

This repository includes a collection of Power BI projects that showcase data modeling, visual analytics, and business insight generation across a variety of domains.

Each project uses real-world or simulated datasets and focuses on transforming raw data into meaningful dashboards and KPIs.

---

## Projects Overview

| Project Name | Topic | Description | Tools / Focus |
|--------------|-------|-------------|----------------|
| **Coffee Sales Analysis** | Sales Analytics | Analyzing trends in coffee beverage sales over time, by type and payment method. Includes forecasting for future sales. | Power Query, DAX, Time Intelligence, Forecasting |
| **Social Media Addiction (Students)** | Social/Behavioral Data | Investigating how students' social media habits affect sleep, mental health, and academic performance. | DAX, Demographic Analysis, Correlation Exploration |
| **Social Media Reach** | Digital Marketing | Evaluating the reach and effectiveness of social media platforms across various audience segments. | Metrics KPIs, Engagement Analysis, Visual Filtering |

